Not saying they’re near the hardest, but you can’t tell me learning material use, setups, stage materials, combos, etc. are “easy”

Obviously he carries, but if you taught someone new to smash:
- building
- stage mining cycles
- TNT/Anvil setups
- Optimal Elytra use
- Crafting table mechanics
- block mechanics
- etc
Sure you can get away with not knowing everything, but getting to high/top level requires this
